// Regression guard: `<` and `>` inside method-call args must parse
// as comparisons (lt/gt), not collide with the operator-shape lookups
// the parser does to dispatch send_method. The arg list here is
// `(a < b, c > d)` -- two comparison expressions, comma-separated.
new x, a, b, c, d in {
  x!y(a < b, c > d).
}
